name: FounderCorps
description: Supporting entrepreneurs in the DC area.
overview:
FounderCorps is a not for profit corporation that is managed by experienced technology entrepreneurs for the benefit of entrepreneurs in Washington, DC, Northern Virginia and suburban Maryland.
